# Price Calculator

This is a simple application that allows you to calculate the minimum price for different payment methods based on the cost price of a product. It also includes a functionality to reset the form for calculating a new item.

## Features
- Calculates the minimum price for payment via Pix, cash, debit, and credit (in various modalities).
- Allows you to reset the form to calculate a new item.

## How to Use
- Enter the product's cost price in the "Enter the cost price" field.
- Click the "Calculate" button to obtain the minimum selling prices for the available payment methods.
- To calculate a new item, click the "Calculate New Item" button.

## Contributing
If you would like to contribute improvements or new features to the Price Calculator, feel free to fork the project and submit your suggestions through pull requests.